title: 07/02/21 DPS Hour 3 Jamie Hector

description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, actor Jamie Hector discusses his career as well as his current projects. Also, center Frank Kaminsky--Big Ten basketball legend and current member of the Phoenix Suns--joins the show to offer his perspective on his team reaching the Finals.
